{"arkId":"cl010115457","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010115457","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Cadran-boussole horizontal","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cadran-boussole horizontal"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1700 - 1800","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10724","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"cadran solaire","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Cet instrument ins\u00e9r\u00e9 dans une bo\u00eete circulaire se compose d\u0027une boussole sur laquelle un anneau inscrit d\u0027une \u00e9chelle horaire, et muni d\u0027un gnomon triangulaire rabattable ( avec un espace apparement r\u00e9serv\u00e9 pour un fil \u00e0 plomb), constitue un cadran solaire utilisable \u00e0 la latitude d\u0027environ 50\u00b0. La boussole poss\u00e8de sur son fond un papier dessin\u00e9 d\u0027une rose des vents \u00e0 trente-deux directions, avec une rosace en son centre et une fleur de lys pour le nord.\r\nSur le revers du couvercle, une table sert \u00e0 convertir en heures communes les heures mesur\u00e9es la nuit \u00e0 la lumi\u00e8re de la Lune. Elle se compose d\u0027un petit disque rotatoire dont l\u0027index pointe vers l\u0027\u00e9chelle de l\u0027\u00e2ge de la Lune sur un grand disque fixe ; un orifice m\u00e9nag\u00e9 dans le disque mobile laisse voir la phase de l\u0027astre correspondant \u00e0 son \u00e2ge.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3","displayDimension":"3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"10,5","displayDimension":"10,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"4,7","displayDimension":"4,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"4,7","displayDimension":"4,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":8,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire = dent (tachet\u00e9)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : alliage cuivreux\r\nMat\u00e9riau : verre\r\nMat\u00e9riau : papier (avec polychromie rouge, noire et bleue)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : soie (verte)","placeOfCreation":"Nuremberg = N\u00fcremberg (Allemagne-\u003EBavi\u00e8re)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Nicolas Landau (1887-1979) ; legs Marcelle Landau, 1980","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Landau, Nicolas","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Mme Landau, Marcelle","note":" (don d\u0027un ensemble de 166 instruments scientifiques, en ex\u00e9cution des volont\u00e9s de son \u00e9poux Nicolas Landau)","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1979","startYear":1979,"endYear":1979},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"22\/11\/1979","startYear":1979,"endYear":1979}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes",